}}

哈德遜郡是紐澤西州內人口密度最高的郡。
* 郡內唯一列入美國百大人口城鎮的城市是[[澤西市|澤西市]]。根據[[美國人口普查局|美國人口普查局]]2012年的估計，排名為全美第75名<ref>[http://files.hawaii.gov/dbedt/census/popestimate/2012-subcounty-population-hawaii/PEP_2012_PEPANNRSIP.US12A.pdf PEPANNRSIP-Geography-United States: Annual Estimates of the Resident Population for Incorporated Places Over 50,000, Ranked by July 1, 2012 Population: April 1, 2010 to July 1, 2012 - United States -- Places Over 50,000 Population 2012 Population Estimates] {{Wayback|url=http://files.hawaii.gov/dbedt/census/popestimate/2012-subcounty-population-hawaii/PEP_2012_PEPANNRSIP.US12A.pdf |date=20131004232920 }}, [[;en:United_States_Census_Bureau|;en:United States Census Bureau]] data archived by the Hawaii Department of Business, Economic Development & Tourism. Accessed October 4, 2013.</ref>。
* 在五萬人以上的城鎮中，[[友聯市|友聯市]]是美國人口密度最高的城鎮<ref>[http://www.demographia.com/db-2000city50kdens.htm 2000 Census: US Municipalities Over 50,000: Ranked by 2000 Density] {{Wayback|url=http://www.demographia.com/db-2000city50kdens.htm |date=20070821000150 }}, accessed March 22, 2007</ref><ref name=StandUp>Al Sullivan. "Stand up and be counted" ''[[The_Union_City_Reporter|The Union City Reporter]]''; January 17, 2010; Page 4</ref>。
* {{le|北博根|North Bergen, New Jersey}}為全美僅次於[[舊金山|舊金山]]的第二多丘密集的城市<ref name=Most>[http://www.hudsonreporter.com/site/news.cfm?BRD=1291&dept_id=523585&newsid=17118972&PAG=461&rfi=9 Most liquor licenses? Bumpiest town? Local municipalities hold unusual distinctions] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hudsonreporter.com/site/news.cfm?BRD=1291&dept_id=523585&newsid=17118972&PAG=461&rfi=9 |date=20080523111437 }}, ''[[Hudson_Reporter|Hudson Reporter]]'', August 27, 2006</ref>。
* {{le|北哈德遜|North Hudson, New Jersey}}是維霍肯到北博根之間城鎮的集合體稱呼，有美國內僅次於[[邁阿密|邁阿密]]的第二大古巴裔美國人人口<ref name=StandUp/>。
* [[澤西市|澤西市]]是美國內族群多樣第21名的城市，但在[[美國東岸|美國東岸]]則是族群多樣最高的城市<ref>[http://www.city-data.com/top35.html Top 100 Most Racially Diverse Cities (pop. 5,000+)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.city-data.com/top35.html |date=20070820184050 }}, accessed February 25, 2007</ref>。
* 哈德遜郡許多人為美國外出生，其中西紐約有65.2%、友聯市有58.7%、古騰堡有48.7%的人口為國外出生<ref>[http://www.city-data.com/top11.html Top 100 Cities with Highest Percentage of Foreign-Born Residents (pop. 5000+)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.city-data.com/top11.html |date=20070817141156 }}, accessed February 25, 2007</ref>。

